It has only one railway station: Nanning Railway Station. From this station, you can catch trains to Liuzhou, Guilin, and Kunming. We provide the train schedule for Naning Railway Station, and it will give you all of the information on trains leaving from and going to Nanning. Find the Nanning train schedule on China Highlights, as we provide a list of trains leaving from and going to Nanning Railway Station.
